    "insights": [
      {
        "id": "insight_1",
        "title_ja": "退職で消える知 — 後継者のいない重要知識",
        "title_en": "Knowledge Walking Out the Door",
        "body_ja": "接着強度の定義(森田)・光学透過率(山本)・医療認証クラス(渡辺)は、いずれも2026年に退職予定の社員が【唯一の保有者】。後継者なしで退職すれば、その意味は永久に失われる。誰が何を知っているかをグラフで所有していれば、退職前に移管できる。",
        "body_en": "Bond Strength (Morita), Optical Transmittance (Yamamoto) and Medical Cert Class (Watanabe) each have a single owner — all retiring in 2026. Without succession, the meaning is lost forever. Owning who-knows-what as a graph lets you transfer it before they leave."
      },
      {
        "id": "insight_2",
        "title_ja": "意味の統治 — 用語が市場ごとに未承認のまま",
        "title_en": "Governing Meaning Across Markets",
        "body_ja": "「医療認証クラス」は北米・日本でのみ承認済みで、欧州・APAC・中南米は未承認。用語(意味)の市場別承認は commit/PR で統治すべき作業。グラフが【どこで未承認か】を一発で示す。",
        "body_en": "'Medical Cert Class' is approved only in North America and Japan — Europe, APAC and Latin America are not. Per-market approval of meaning is governed work (commit/PR). The graph shows exactly where the gaps are."
      },
      {
        "id": "insight_3",
        "title_ja": "コンプラ横断 — 規制の影響範囲と責任者が一発",
        "title_en": "Compliance, End to End",
        "body_ja": "架空のEU製品環境指令2026は、防護マスク・コーティング剤・接着フィルム・医療ドレッシングと欧州市場を規制対象とし、責任は法務のMüller。規制Xの影響製品と責任者をグラフで即特定できる。",
        "body_en": "The (fictional) EU Eco Directive 2026 governs Respirator Mask, Coating Agent, Adhesive Film and Medical Dressing across Europe, owned by Müller in Legal. The graph instantly maps a regulation's blast radius and its owner."
      }
    ]
  },
